---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="90-Day Chatbot Profit Promise | Scott Armbruster" description="3X return on your AI chatbot investment in 90 days or get a full refund. Transparent metrics, weekly reporting, real results.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
          Risk-Free AI Implementation
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          90-Day Chatbot
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">
            Profit Promise
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-200 mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-light">
          3X return on your investment or you get a full refund
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          I build AI chatbots that pay for themselves. If yours doesn't generate at least
          3X its cost in new revenue or savings within 90 days, I'll refund every dollar.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Claim Your Guarantee
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/calculators/chatbot-roi"
            class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Calculate Your ROI First
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Promise -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">3X</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Return Guarantee</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Your chatbot must generate at least 3X its total cost in measurable value within 90 days
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">100%</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Money-Back Refund</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            If we miss the 3X target, you get a full refund of the implementation fee. No questions asked.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-3">Weekly</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Transparent Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            You'll see every conversation, every lead, and every dollar attributed to your chatbot
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">How the Guarantee Works</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          Simple terms. No fine print. Here's exactly what happens.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">We Define Success Together</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 mb-2">
              Before writing a single line of code, we agree on specific, measurable targets. These typically include:
            </p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>New leads captured after hours</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Support tickets resolved automatically</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Appointments booked without staff</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Staff hours freed up per week</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">I Build and Deploy Your Chatbot</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">
              Typical timeline is 2 weeks from kickoff to live deployment. Your chatbot is trained on your business data, FAQs, services, and brand voice. It integrates with your existing website, CRM, and booking systems.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">We Track Everything for 90 Days</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">
              You get a live metrics dashboard showing every conversation, every lead captured, and every dollar of value generated. Weekly reports land in your inbox every Monday morning so you always know exactly where things stand.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Day 90: We Settle Up</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">
              If your chatbot generated 3X or more in value, you keep it running and I transition to a low-cost maintenance plan. If it didn't hit the target, I refund your implementation fee in full. You keep the chatbot either way.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Math -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">The Math Is Simple</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          Here's what 3X looks like for a typical small business chatbot
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
            <span class="text-slate-300">Chatbot implementation cost</span>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold">$1,500</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
            <span class="text-slate-300">3X target (90 days)</span>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold">$4,500</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
            <span class="text-slate-300">That's roughly per month</span>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold">$1,500/mo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-2">
            <span class="text-slate-300">Results vary by business</span>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400">We'll model yours</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-6 text-center">
          Every business is different. We define specific targets together before starting.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Qualification -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Is This Right for Your Business?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          The guarantee works best for businesses that meet these criteria
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-green-500/30 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400">Good Fit</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300">You get 500+ monthly website visitors</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300">Your average deal value is $500+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300">You miss leads after hours or on weekends</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300">Your team spends 10+ hours/week on repetitive customer questions</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-400">Not Yet</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-400">Pre-revenue or fewer than 100 monthly visitors</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-400">Very low transaction values (under $50 average)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-400">No existing website or online presence</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-400">Purely offline business model</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Put Your Chatbot to the Test?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Book a free discovery call. I'll review your business, run the numbers, and tell you honestly
        whether a chatbot can hit the 3X target for your situation.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          Book Discovery Call
        </a>
        <a
          href="/calculators/chatbot-roi"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Try the ROI Calculator
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
